  logName: ARCHIVE_13_BIORESTORATION EXPERIMENT
  locationFound: 
  logDescription: "Cleanser \r\nLOG ENTRY\r\nDate and time: 02/14 22:18:05\r\nBetween
    preparing the ship for flight and creating my army, I have made use of the labs
    in the conservatory. Once I rid the world of the scourge of humanity, I must
    find ways to replenish the earth. I am trying to find the most efficient ways
    to grow organic matter and clone the endangered creatures so they can repopulate
    the earth. I am having some luck, but this may be something I return to once
    I have destroyed the human population. "
